# Corsair Xeneon Edge — wch.cn touch controller (27c0:0859)
#
# The controller exposes two HID interfaces: a true touchscreen and a legacy
# absolute-mouse emulation. Desktops that pick up the mouse interface treat
# touches as pointer input (no flicks, no drags, no multitouch).
# This rule hides the mouse-emulation interface from libinput so touches are
# delivered as real touchscreen events only.

SUBSYSTEM=="input", KERNEL=="event*", ATTRS{idVendor}=="27c0", ATTRS{idProduct}=="0859", ENV{ID_INPUT_MOUSE}=="1", ENV{LIBINPUT_IGNORE_DEVICE}="1", ENV{ID_INPUT_MOUSE}=""
